      <abstract>
        <p>A heterocycle, 4-[(1,3-benzothiazol-2-ylimino)methyl]phenyl dodecanoate, was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR, elemental analysis and MS spectroscopic data are presented. This new compound exhibited smectic A phase.</p>
      </abstract>
      <kwd-group>
        <kwd>4-[(1,3-benzothiazol-2-ylimino)methyl]phenyl dodecanoate</kwd>
